      "why_it_matters": "The component uses inline React.CSSProperties objects (barStyle, tagStyle, tagCloseStyle, clearBtnStyle). Testing exact color values makes tests brittle to design changes. Testing structural properties (flex layout) is more meaningful but still couples to implementation."
